Adjancency matrix :
 amader jokhon kono node er sthe onno node er connection ache ki na ver kore hobe
 tokhon adjancency matrix lagbe .. weight er khetre adj mat er per cell er amra oi node er weight rakte pari.. 

 adjacency list:
 eti ekti vector array.. means je .. int a[5] bolte amra buji je a namok ([]) array er 5 ti index 
 per index er ekek ti int data type er value ache .. vector <int> a[5] bolte per index ekek ti vector and oi vector er data type hobe int data typedef
 ar jodi weight rakhte jai then vector <pair<int,int>> a[5] er data type dibo int mane se vector er data type er moto behave korbe and er index e ekti kore pair rakhbe and sei pair er data type gulo hobe int


 edge list :
 amder jokhon edge lists nie kaj koret hobe tokhon edge list use korbo .. like bellman ford ., warshaw algo edder moto..
 vector <pair<int,int>> v/// ar weighted graph e edge er sthe weight thkle pair or pair ba vector of vector diyeo weight ba cost neya jay but complex onek
 tai alada class Edge baniye  vector <Edge > evabe push kore 3 ta data eksthe neya hoi


 Matrix -> adj_list
 Matrix -> edge 
 
 adj_list ->matrix
 adj_list ->edge
  
 edge -> matrix
 edge ->adj_list
 